    "title": "Teams QuickLinks — Context-Aware Quick Links Tab",
    "shortDescription": "A lightweight Microsoft Teams Tab that displays context-aware quick links per team and channel, driven by a static JSON config — no backend, no database, no Graph permissions required.",
