    "longDescription": [
      "A lightweight Microsoft Teams Tab application that displays context-aware quick links based on the current team and channel.",
      "Links are resolved from a static JSON configuration, supporting team-level, channel-level, and default fallback link sets.",
      "Users can search, pin, and unpin links — all without a backend, database, or Microsoft Graph permissions."
